{"tid":349142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳志健回港3日又走失　警方尋回暫住北區醫院","createTime":"2017-08-06T10:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T11:20:41.000Z","uid":48294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa76a7abc5d040f1c44b17ef5cb5357d22035a81","tid":349142,"uid":48294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/110154?utm_content=buffer12cff&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F110154%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer12cff%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=qmBGhWIfcDOk6vQx21bcvI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=24bc7eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/110154?utm_content=buffer12cff&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n2006年一度人間蒸發11年的香港商人陳志健，今年2月在內地尋回後，本月初獲送回香港，但竟再失蹤。他於今日（6日）凌晨在上水古洞流連，有市民發現並報警，警方尋回他後，暫把他送至北區醫院。消息指陳的太太仍在內地，警方暫未能與她聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/749233/xlarge/071b9a3d92420d1c75ed8acd6d909ef8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F749233%2Fxlarge%2F071b9a3d92420d1c75ed8acd6d909ef8.jpg&h=d24edf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方今日凌晨1時左右接獲市民報案，指一名老翁於上水古洞青山公路近河上鄉路的巴士站附近流連，警員到場後尋獲該名長者，對方不能話語，身上無任何身分證明文件及金錢，只帶着數張紙。警員循紙上身分證號碼證實老翁為陳志健，將他送往北區醫院。據知陳志健有兩名社工跟進，而警方曾到陳志健於灣仔的寓所拍門，但無人應門，也未聯絡到陳太或其他家人，陳太的友人稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">她目前不在香港，仍在內地。</span><br />\n<br />\n究竟係啲屋企人戇鳩定特登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea4d4ce5ccbbe9d289fcbed7ac3ab5e64b4f88c","tid":349142,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:31:11.000Z","msg":"點解要救佢返香港？大陸咁好住，留係大陸做乞衣好過啦"},{"pid":"19798af5c119e400199b2a7ce04807d5eb68a2a4","tid":349142,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"住灣仔但係係上水古洞游盪係咩玩法"},{"pid":"def48346df9b566043bd6e4479a81b8d24a87550","tid":349142,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/110154?utm_content=buffer12cff&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F110154%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer12cff%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=qmBGhWIfcDOk6vQx21bcvI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=24bc7eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/110154?utm_content=buffer12cff&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n2006年一度人間蒸發11年的香港商人陳志健，今年2月在內地尋回後，本月初獲送回香港，但竟再失蹤。他於今日（6日）凌晨在上水古洞流連，有市民發現並報警，警方尋回他後，暫把他送至北區醫院。消息指陳的太太仍在內地，警方暫未能與她聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/749233/xlarge/071b9a3d92420d1c75ed8acd6d909ef8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F749233%2Fxlarge%2F071b9a3d92420d1c75ed8acd6d909ef8.jpg&h=d24edf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方今日凌晨1時左右接獲市民報案，指一名老翁於上水古洞青山公路近河上鄉路的巴士站附近流連，警員到場後尋獲該名長者，對方不能話語，身上無任何身分證明文件及金錢，只帶着數張紙。警員循紙上身分證號碼證實老翁為陳志健，將他送往北區醫院。據知陳志健有兩名社工跟進，而警方曾到陳志健於灣仔的寓所拍門，但無人應門，也未聯絡到陳太或其他家人，陳太的友人稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">她目前不在香港，仍在內地。</span><br />\n<br />\n究竟係啲屋企人戇鳩定特登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似話搬左去大陸住"},{"pid":"f2aa069020be992dba5e895bd83213da4f3942eb","tid":349142,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"擺到明係大陸婆呃哂佢錢 佢癲左就番大陸流浪 而家比人搵番 個大陸婆就番大陸避風頭"}]}